.876 459 7(2), and v_c(3,12^2) =\n5.033 078 49(4), the precision being comparable or superior to the best\nsimulation results. More generally, we trace the critical manifolds in the real\n(q,v) plane and discuss the intricate structure of the phase diagram in the\nantiferromagnetic (v<0) region.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Nov 2012 08:35:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
